    use OntologyGraph.getAncestorsStream(Object) if you do not wish to see the source in the stream or OntologyGraph.extendWithAncestors(Object, boolean) if you want to include the source. However, consider using OntologyGraph.extendWithAncestors(Object, boolean, Collection) instead.

    use OntologyGraph.getChildren(Object) if you do not wish to see source in the iterable or OntologyGraph.extendWithChildren(Object, boolean) if you need the source in the result.
